      "full_name": "Lukyanovich Andrei Yulyanovich",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "Major General Andrei Lukyanovich is a military pilot, Commander of the Belarusian Air Force and Air Defence Forces/Chief of Aviation of Belarus, and Commander of military unit 06752/Machulishchi airfield. In this capacity, he participated in the joint military exercises of Russia and Belarus preceding the military build-up at the Ukrainian border which prepared the military aggression against Ukraine of 24 February 2022. He is part of the Belarusian army, which has supported Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
